item.title: Initial feedback on Fuji X100S
item.description: My X100S has finally arrived. First time I get a brand new camera that I’m already familiar with. Many reviews have now been written on this fantastic camera. I just wanted to share some of my initial thoughts based upon my first experiments done at night and under difficult light.
